The paper discusses a new unsupervised cost function for machine learning, which is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. The other likely categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as the paper discusses applications of the new cost function to various types of datasets and domains.
